{"tid":546674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男友求婚成功   鍾欣潼IG晒巨形鑽戒","createTime":"2018-01-31T17:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T16:20:01.000Z","uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"abb561be7314af0dccf748a72340fb738242edae","tid":546674,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T17:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180201/large/1517417011_3bff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180201%2Flarge%2F1517417011_3bff.jpg&h=c8a2b5bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180201/large/1517416720_6630.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180201%2Flarge%2F1517416720_6630.jpg&h=3618a362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180201/large/1517416728_575f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180201%2Flarge%2F1517416728_575f.jpg&h=fa68fefb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTwins兩位成員去年先前被爆拍拖，其中阿嬌鍾欣潼同台灣男友有「醫界王陽明」之稱嘅賴弘國拍拖。<br />\n<br />\n阿嬌喺上週度過37歲生日又傳嚟好消息，今日凌晨佢喺ig貼上左手無名指戴上巨形鑽戒嘅相片，仲留言：「下一站幸福！」。<br />\n<br />\n男方透過友人獨家回應台灣《蘋果》：「我不是藝人，希望低調，但會努力作好自己的事業，給阿嬌最大的幸福，也希望大家能給予祝福。」<br />\n<br />\n阿嬌答應男友求婚，好友阿Sa亦有更新ig貼上同阿嬌嘅合照並留言：「千言萬語在心中！」似乎記係戥好姊妹開心。<br />\n<br />\n鍾舒漫接受《蘋果》電話訪問表示已恭喜師姐：「頭先我有send whatsapp畀佢，因為其實我都替佢好興奮，我就恭喜佢囉。」問到阿嬌點回覆？Sherman表示：「我估呢刻好多人恭喜佢，佢就say咗個thank you，佢都好忙覆message。」"},{"pid":"b8eac0c91a52322555f9a55200ae0db13a44bbed","tid":546674,"uid":17008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T18:21:35.000Z","msg":"之前節目度都催婚咁話想快d生仔<br />\n有無一年拍左？<br />\n希望佢搵得岩"},{"pid":"df0fed7ba337fac6d8101ca3eee59bf86e5c350c","tid":546674,"uid":24044,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T18:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"ht